{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783744633793,"sessionID":"ses_0b0929e35ffeiPmK0rQRK8nw1B","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_8524b2f680fb45d4b1e14d1e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — glm52 Lineage\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| Run | Focus | newInfoRatio | Findings | Status |\n|-----|-------|-------------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | sk-git, sk-code, system-spec-kit hook/plugin candidates | 1.0 | 4 | complete |\n| 2 | sk-doc, sk-prompt, sk-design hook/plugin candidates | 0.8 | 5 | complete |\n| 3 | system-deep-loop, mcp-code-mode, cli-external, underused surfaces | 0.7 | 5 | complete |\n| 4 | Cross-cutting unified hooks, blast-radius ranking, backlog assembly | 0.5 | 2 | complete |\n| 5 | Completeness verification and convergence | 0.3 | 2 | complete |\n\n## Question Status\n\n5/5 answered\n\n| ID | Question | Status |\n|----|----------|--------|\n| KQ-1 | Which skills have latent behaviors promotable to hooks/plugins? | Answered |\n| KQ-2 | Which have proven runtime contracts? | Answered |\n| KQ-3 | Which OpenCode surfaces are underused? | Answered |\n| KQ-4 | Which Claude surfaces have gaps? | Answered |\n| KQ-5 | Blast radius distribution? | Answered |\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\n| Direction | Values |\n|-----------|--------|\n| Last 3 ratios | 0.7 → 0.5 → 0.3 |\n| Trend | Descending (converging) |\n\n## Dead Ends\n\n- Deep-loop dispatch enforcement — already covered by mk-deep-loop-guard.js\n- Spec-memory continuity injection — already covered by mk-spec-memory.js\n- Skill routing — already covered by mk-skill-advisor.js\n- Goal-state management — already covered by mk-goal.js\n- Individual system-spec-kit/rules/* as standalone hooks — too granular\n- MCP tooling doctor.sh as SessionStart hooks — better as /doctor command targets\n- quality-kpi.sh as per-edit hook — too heavy\n\n## Lifecycle\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Session ID | fanout-glm52-1783743995827-g7k8yl |\n| Lineage Mode | new |\n| Generation | 1 |\n| Stop Reason | converged |\n| Total Iterations | 5 |\n| Total Candidates | 18 |\n\n## Next Focus\n\nCONVERGED — synthesis complete\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/glm52/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/glm52/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/glm52/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1783744633790,"end":1783744633792}},"id":"prt_f4f771bbc0018pog9v5x4xh92p","sessionID":"ses_0b0929e35ffeiPmK0rQRK8nw1B","messageID":"msg_f4f76e47b001ttVgcjZjaTZTMN"}}
